additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Medium-Chain Triglyceride (MCT) Powder (38%), Green Coffee Powder Extract (20%), Vegan Capsule (Hypromellose and Titanium Dioxide), Calcium Hydrogen Phosphate, L-Carnitine (6.8%), Guarana Seed Powder Extract (6.8%), Cayenne Pepper (1.4%), Silicon Dioxide, Magnesium Stearate, Microcrystalline Cellulose. Contains caffeine (approximately 22mg per 2 capsules OR 11 mg per capsule).

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Not suitable for children under the age of 15 or for pregnant or lactating women. Not a sole source of nutrition and should be consumed in conjunction with a nutritious diet and physical exercise program. Should be used under medical or dietetic supervision. Formulated Supplementary Sports Food. Do not use if tamper-evident seal is broken or missing.
